# Generated artifacts — keep the dirs (via .gitkeep) but ignore contents on main.
# Phase 3: state/ contents are persisted on the `state` branch via the workflow.
# Phase 3: out/ artifacts are uploaded as GHA artifacts per-run.
state/*
!state/.gitkeep
out/*
!out/.gitkeep
